This video was made possible thanks to everyone on the Simple History Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/simplehistory

Europe’s expansion across the world forever changed the lives of Indigenous peoples. In this video, we explore how colonization, resource extraction, and cultural suppression reshaped entire civilizations, and the lasting impact still felt today.
